OL,12,G1720 Four in a Bed
OL,13,     FIt's the final day and the B&Bers
OL,14,     Fmeet one last time to settle some
OL,15,     Fscores and find out how much
OL,16,     Fthey've been paid. After some
OL,17,     Fhosting, roasting and dust
OL,18,     Fdisputes, the winner's announced.
